divs: Sighting DetailsHeaded south on i75 just passed i675 seen directly in front of me one streak of fire headed in a southerly direction. It split into two streaks of fire then disappeared. Then I looked to my left and there were 5 white arbs floating in random positions. The 2 on the bottom didnt move much but the other 3 moved, disappeared, reappeared and sometimes orbited on another. This lasted for about 5 min then they disappeared.
Summary: 5 floating white lights and a streak of fire that split into 2
trends: There have been 10 other sightings in Springboro
